{"about_the_game":"Shard Shuffle plunges you into a world that combines strategic skill and puzzle-solving. The goal is clear: strategically place pieces with various properties on the game board to destroy other elements and score points. Each piece has a certain number of life points and a distinct attack type. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game reaches its conclusion when the board can no longer accommodate new pieces. This is why methodical planning of your strategy is crucial to optimally eliminate pieces. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nHowever, piece destruction is only part of the equation to boost your high score. A combo system awards you additional points when you eliminate multiple pieces in one go. This allows you to obtain a highly explosive bomb, ideal for clearing a part of the board cluttered with pieces. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game also features a challenge system, adding a dose of excitement by presenting random challenges to earn more points and Shards. Once collected, these Shards unlock customization elements to enrich the gaming experience according to your preferences.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Start of journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2742490/7de1795c4be15fdb7ec6cf30700d4451f85576f6.jpg"},{"name":"Too easy for me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2742490/3705f971ecf32702682f4bed09cc28751df6053c.jpg"},{"name":"Who can beat that?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2742490/6fb495a869532be658efc7c6e977af686b3d44ee.jpg"},{"name":"Lucky day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2742490/b73bcfc4eca9f7603b7b75c32d5c818f978f545f.jpg"},{"name":"Is there anyone here?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2742490/6ccdfd04e9998b3cac37454ca1f32430eda37f40.jpg"},{"name":"Superiority","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/p